# Cortex v2 — Universal AI Brain

Multi-transport memory daemon. SQLite + Ollama embeddings + per-agent profiles.

## Structure
- src/daemon.js — HTTP :7437 + MCP stdio server
- src/brain.js — Core logic (index, recall, store, forget)
- src/embeddings.js — Ollama nomic-embed-text vectors
- src/compiler.js — Boot prompt compiler with token budgets
- src/conflict.js — Cross-agent conflict detection and resolution
- src/db.js — SQLite via sql.js (WASM)
- src/cli.js — CLI wrapper (talks to daemon over HTTP)

## Conventions
- Node.js 24+, zero deps except sql.js
- Manual arg parsing (no commander)
- All Windows paths via process.env.USERPROFILE
- Port 7437 for HTTP, 11434 for Ollama
- Auth token at ~/.cortex/cortex.token for POST endpoints
- Conflict check before surprise filter on store path
